The resetObfuscateFlowExclusions Statement

The ZKM Script resetObfuscateFlowExclusions statement removes all exclusions that may have been set by preceding obfuscateFlowExclude statements.

Example

resetObfuscateFlowExclusions;

Syntax

"resetObfuscateFlowExclusions" ";"
